Content:: David Dekker (born 2 February 1998) is a Dutch cyclist, who currently rides for UCI WorldTeam Team Jumbo–Visma.[3][4] He is the son of former professional cyclist Erik Dekker. In May 2021, Dekker was named in the startlist for the 2021 Giro d'Italia.[5] This biographical article related to a Dutch cycling person born in the 1990s is a stub.
